<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='764000' id='t-764000'>And on top of it, we have this memory system called the neocortex.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='767000' id='t-767000'>And the memory system is sitting over the sensory part of the brain.</span>
