<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='813000' id='t-813000'>This is the most important slide of my talk, so I'll dwell on it a little bit.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='816000' id='t-816000'>And so, all the time you say, oh, I can predict the things.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='820000' id='t-820000'>And if you're a rat and you go through a maze, and then you learn the maze,</span>
